column4: Tesla cranks up big battery in Australia
column5: MELBOURNE Tesla Inc  has completed construction of the world's largest lithium ion battery in Australia  putting it on track to meet a 100-day deadline for switching the battery packs on  the South Australian government said on Thursday.
